# Specialty Applications

## Overview

Specialty applications utilize advanced polyester films engineered for optical clarity, security, decorative appearance, and specialized functional performance. These products are characterized by high value addition and lower production volumes.

---

## Market Analysis

- Accounts for approximately 10–15% of the specialty PET film market.

- High-margin segment driven by technological innovation rather than volume.

- Increasing investment in premium packaging, anti-counterfeit solutions, and smart materials is supporting market growth.

---

## Major End-use Industries

- Sequins & Decorative Films

- Optical Films

- Security Films

- Construction Materials

---

## Key Growth Drivers

- Premium consumer products

